{"tid":1077902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人屋企會掛全家福？","createTime":"2019-03-26T01:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T03:39:04.000Z","uid":95245,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8f0bb00b83f446d3c3ba88ed3a7e3904c0c901","tid":1077902,"uid":95245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:59:31.000Z","msg":"以前見到人地屋企有張全家福<br />\n會覺得好奇怪<br />\n但係依家大個之後<br />\n覺得老豆老母越嚟越老<br />\n如果以後一個唔覺意真係走咗<br />\n我怕會無啲野係到留念而成為遺憾<br />\n其實係咪應該襯佢地健健康康<br />\n就的佢地去影相？<br />\n<br />\n但係衰在自己on9毒撚性格<br />\n平時又同屋企人無兩句<br />\n無喇喇叫佢地去影全家福好奇怪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0720d83439fed468cadedc4a9789d1918981851","tid":1077902,"uid":209301,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:02:24.000Z","msg":"話有特價，好抵，一家人去影吓咁<br />\n大家著靚靚去影，好開心"},{"pid":"3cd814befaec116baba658b8447487d3433ff679","tid":1077902,"uid":838,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:05:01.000Z","msg":"影啦，唔好俾自己後悔"},{"pid":"c3b0f4b1e0527bd1c0772c6bbbef344a634305b6","tid":1077902,"uid":33483,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"影一次最多咪三幾千 但你唔影就可能會後悔一世"},{"pid":"8c7f0b5c3c9c7176e2a2421c478072116805caeb","tid":1077902,"uid":30708,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:07:29.000Z","msg":"上兩年我地全家人，連埋阿哥老婆加BB去影，<br />\n而家離咗婚，D相好撚眼冤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828fd60161b60a2d4851d7ccf3eecaa2a406184d","tid":1077902,"uid":243649,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"唔影就等後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1efd30bb2aebcca53a80e8a9a01b47c663a34db","tid":1077902,"uid":144529,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"我屋企全家福一年影4次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一家4口，邊個生日都影一次"},{"pid":"845eff7ffbe9ca4a71e955dd1fdaac3a191e0abf","tid":1077902,"uid":181905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:29:46.000Z","msg":"放咗一家人去日本玩概相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b998626106e8bcdf305fe7952ba378cfe21be5","tid":1077902,"uid":95245,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:49:56.000Z","msg":"屋企得兩兄弟 同老豆老母<br />\n兩個都媾唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上影完都唔會眼冤既<br />\n當留念用途啫"},{"pid":"d8d820937b1943a60f85265f7e59ee0762357aa8","tid":1077902,"uid":95245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"如果真係去影嘅話<br />\n普遍價位係幾多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbd6c39ec48a17b7f71d34d5cb01de15bcbb79a","tid":1077902,"uid":95245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:40:05.000Z","msg":"呢個問題困擾左我成年<br />\n有無人可以狠狠咁樣打醒我<br />\n同我講失去左先嚟後悔係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8259639bc9c35b14824ce00db179389b40534ee","tid":1077902,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T18:19:59.000Z","msg":"支持巴打同屋企人影<br />\n唔好將來後悔"},{"pid":"38268cdecfaa18854fe7fbbf0c854e67f7303e3f","tid":1077902,"uid":145067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"有全家福不過冇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣未出世"},{"pid":"29ad3a46cf9a61ee5d15b6cbe53eee739b5b8697","tid":1077902,"uid":95245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38268cdecfaa18854fe7fbbf0c854e67f7303e3f","tid":1077902,"uid":145067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"有全家福不過冇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />